@DeviceManagement_HostAddress = http://localhost:5084
@Bearer = paste_jwt_here

### Search devices (MongoDB text index: name, manufacturer, processor, RAM)
GET {{DeviceManagement_HostAddress}}/api/devices/search?q=surface+16
Authorization: Bearer {{Bearer}}

###

### Generate device description (Ollama: ollama serve + ollama pull llama3.2)
POST {{DeviceManagement_HostAddress}}/api/devices/generate-description
Authorization: Bearer {{Bearer}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "iPhone 17 Pro",
  "manufacturer": "Apple",
  "type": "Phone",
  "os": "iOS",
  "osVersion": "26",
  "processor": "A19 Pro",
  "ramGb": 12
}

###
